{"image_id": "ZBRA_2008_page_30", "image_size": [1650, 1275], "ocr": [{"text": "17", "bbox": [75.0, 1222.9, 88.9, 1239.2]}, {"text": "Operating expense changes for SPG in 2008, compared to the same periods in 2007, are", "bbox": [75.0, 146.7, 780.0, 166.7]}, {"text": "due to the following (in thousands):", "bbox": [75.0, 167.5, 364.7, 187.5]}, {"text": "Three Months Ended", "bbox": [435.4, 194.0, 604.8, 212.0]}, {"text": "Year Ended", "bbox": [695.6, 194.0, 785.4, 212.0]}, {"text": "December 31, 2008", "bbox": [445.4, 212.7, 604.9, 230.7]}, {"text": "December 31, 2008", "bbox": [630.8, 212.7, 785.4, 230.7]}, {"text": "Payroll and benefit costs", "bbox": [75.0, 238.4, 276.8, 258.3]}, {"text": "$(1,847)", "bbox": [542.2, 238.4, 610.1, 258.3]}, {"text": "$  3,530", "bbox": [723.9, 238.4, 785.4, 258.3]}, {"text": "Trade show expenses", "bbox": [75.0, 265.5, 249.3, 285.4]}, {"text": "(680)", "bbox": [564.4, 265.5, 610.1, 285.4]}, {"text": "(1,013)", "bbox": [738.9, 265.5, 791.0, 285.4]}, {"text": "Advertising and market development fund costs", "bbox": [75.0, 292.5, 457.7, 312.5]}, {"text": "(744)", "bbox": [565.9, 292.5, 610.1, 312.5]}, {"text": "1,637", "bbox": [743.3, 292.5, 785.4, 312.5]}, {"text": "Professional services cost", "bbox": [75.0, 319.6, 288.2, 339.6]}, {"text": "578", "bbox": [572.0, 319.6, 604.7, 339.6]}, {"text": "1,890", "bbox": [742.8, 319.6, 785.4, 339.6]}, {"text": "Information technology expenses", "bbox": [75.0, 346.7, 348.8, 366.7]}, {"text": "(646)", "bbox": [564.2, 346.7, 610.1, 366.7]}, {"text": "(1,794)", "bbox": [738.1, 346.7, 791.0, 366.7]}, {"text": "Sales meeting expenses", "bbox": [75.0, 373.8, 274.0, 393.8]}, {"text": "—", "bbox": [583.4, 373.8, 604.6, 393.8]}, {"text": "1,508", "bbox": [743.1, 373.8, 785.4, 393.8]}, {"text": "Stock based compensation expenses", "bbox": [75.0, 400.9, 376.5, 420.8]}, {"text": "(970)", "bbox": [565.2, 400.9, 610.1, 420.8]}, {"text": "(2,770)", "bbox": [737.0, 400.9, 791.0, 420.8]}, {"text": "Exit and restructuring costs", "bbox": [75.0, 428.0, 300.9, 447.9]}, {"text": "6,005", "bbox": [557.0, 428.0, 604.6, 447.9]}, {"text": "16,489", "bbox": [733.1, 428.0, 785.4, 447.9]}, {"text": "Impairment charges", "bbox": [75.0, 455.0, 240.7, 475.0]}, {"text": "14,680", "bbox": [548.2, 455.0, 604.7, 475.0]}, {"text": "14,680", "bbox": [733.5, 455.0, 785.4, 475.0]}, {"text": "Gain on sale of assets", "bbox": [75.0, 482.1, 254.2, 502.1]}, {"text": "—", "bbox": [583.4, 482.1, 604.7, 502.1]}, {"text": "1,347", "bbox": [743.3, 482.1, 785.4, 502.1]}, {"text": "Facility relocation costs", "bbox": [75.0, 509.2, 269.1, 529.2]}, {"text": "—", "bbox": [583.4, 509.2, 604.7, 529.2]}, {"text": "1,092", "bbox": [743.5, 509.2, 785.4, 529.2]}, {"text": "Other changes", "bbox": [75.0, 536.3, 193.7, 556.2]}, {"text": "(1,194)", "bbox": [553.8, 536.3, 610.2, 556.2]}, {"text": "(629)", "bbox": [752.1, 536.3, 791.0, 556.2]}, {"text": "Total increases", "bbox": [85.5, 563.4, 223.7, 583.3]}, {"text": "$15,182", "bbox": [541.1, 563.4, 604.7, 583.3]}, {"text": "$33,273", "bbox": [722.5, 563.4, 785.4, 583.3]}, {"text": "The 2008 payroll and benefit cost increase includes approximately $550,000 for", "bbox": [75.0, 605.1, 707.7, 625.0]}, {"text": "severance not related to the exit activities. Exit costs relate to the transfer of our printer", "bbox": [75.0, 625.9, 769.6, 645.8]}, {"text": "manufacturing to a third-party manufacturer and the closure of our Warwick, Rhode Island", "bbox": [75.0, 646.7, 796.3, 666.7]}, {"text": "supplies manufacturing facility. Restructuring costs relate to organization changes made", "bbox": [75.0, 667.6, 781.2, 687.5]}, {"text": "in December 2008. See Note 22 to the Consolidated Financial Statements included in this", "bbox": [75.0, 688.4, 783.3, 708.3]}, {"text": "Annual Report on Form 10-K for a more detailed discussion of the exit and restructuring", "bbox": [75.0, 709.2, 775.1, 729.2]}, {"text": "costs.  Facility relocation costs relate to the move of our High Wycombe, UK facility into", "bbox": [75.0, 730.1, 774.0, 750.0]}, {"text": "a new location. Impairment charges relate to the write-down of intellectual property", "bbox": [75.0, 750.9, 745.4, 770.8]}, {"text": "because of changes in valuations related to current economic conditions and the business", "bbox": [75.0, 771.7, 792.2, 791.7]}, {"text": "outlook. See Note 13 of the Consolidated Financial Statements included in this Annual", "bbox": [75.0, 792.6, 760.2, 812.5]}, {"text": "Report on Form 10-K for a more detailed discussion of the asset impairment charges.", "bbox": [75.0, 813.4, 753.1, 833.3]}, {"text": "Absent the exit and restructuring costs and impairment charges, the fourth quarter", "bbox": [75.0, 834.2, 736.4, 854.2]}, {"text": "reductions in expenses reflect the cost reduction program initiated during the quarter.", "bbox": [75.0, 855.1, 756.0, 875.0]}, {"text": "During 2008, we completed a sale and leaseback transaction for our manufacturing", "bbox": [75.0, 894.6, 743.6, 914.6]}, {"text": "facility located in Camarillo, California.  Zebra received net proceeds of $14,796,000", "bbox": [75.0, 915.5, 745.7, 935.4]}, {"text": "against a net book value of $10,669,000. Of the $4,127,000 gain, $3,006,000 was deferred", "bbox": [75.0, 936.3, 784.2, 956.3]}, {"text": "and will be applied against future rental payments, and $1,121,000 was recognized in", "bbox": [75.0, 957.1, 755.2, 977.1]}, {"text": "general and administrative expenses.", "bbox": [75.0, 978.0, 375.2, 997.9]}, {"text": "Enterprise Solutions Group (in thousands, except percentages)", "bbox": [843.8, 146.7, 1346.1, 166.7]}, {"text": "Three Months Ended", "bbox": [1103.8, 181.4, 1271.9, 203.6]}, {"text": "Percent of\t Percent of", "bbox": [1367.4, 185.6, 1547.9, 203.6]}, {"text": "December 31,", "bbox": [1134.3, 198.1, 1248.1, 220.3]}, {"text": "Percent", "bbox": [1280.2, 202.3, 1346.5, 220.3]}, {"text": "Net Sales", "bbox": [1374.7, 202.3, 1454.9, 220.3]}, {"text": "Net Sales", "bbox": [1472.6, 202.3