.1, 1167.1, 552.1]}, {"text": "26,121", "bbox": [1205.5, 532.1, 1260.9, 552.1]}, {"text": "NM", "bbox": [1313.0, 532.1, 1346.3, 552.1]}, {"text": "230.4", "bbox": [1408.3, 532.1, 1454.6, 552.1]}, {"text": "74.1", "bbox": [1516.4, 532.1, 1547.9, 552.1]}, {"text": "Operating loss", "bbox": [843.8, 559.2, 977.1, 579.2]}, {"text": "$(165,966)", "bbox": [1087.7, 559.2, 1172.7, 579.2]}, {"text": "$(11,255)", "bbox": [1192.7, 559.2, 1266.4, 579.2]}, {"text": "NM", "bbox": [1313.0, 559.2, 1346.3, 579.2]}, {"text": "(176.1)", "bbox": [1403.7, 559.2, 1460.2, 579.2]}, {"text": "(31.9)", "bbox": [1511.6, 559.2, 1553.5, 579.2]}, {"text": "During 2007 and 2008, Zebra acquired four companies which have been combined", "bbox": [843.8, 600.9, 1506.3, 620.8]}, {"text": "to make up our Enterprise Solutions Group (ESG). On January 25, 2007, we acquired", "bbox": [843.8, 621.7, 1520.3, 641.7]}, {"text": "WhereNet Corp., a provider of active radio frequency identification (RFID) based", "bbox": [843.8, 642.6, 1489.5, 662.5]}, {"text": "wireless solutions used to track and manage enterprise assets. On July 2, 2007, we", "bbox": [843.8, 663.4, 1508.2, 683.3]}, {"text": "acquired proveo AG, a provider of complete hardware and software systems for tracking", "bbox": [843.8, 684.2, 1557.2, 704.2]}, {"text": "motorized vehicles using global positioning systems (GPS). On December 14, 2007,", "bbox": [843.8, 705.1, 1512.5, 725.0]}, {"text": "we acquired Navis Holdings, LLC, a provider of software solutions to optimize the flow", "bbox": [843.8, 725.9, 1538.3, 745.8]}, {"text": "of goods through marine terminals and other operations managing cargo movement", "bbox": [843.8, 746.7, 1525.2, 766.7]}, {"text": "through ports and intermodal facilities. On April 1, 2008, we acquired Multispectral", "bbox": [843.8, 767.6, 1510.8, 787.5]}, {"text": "Solutions Inc., a global provider of ultra wideband (UWB) real-time locating systems and", "bbox": [843.8, 788.4, 1557.4, 808.3]}, {"text": "other UWB-based technology. Together, these companies give Zebra the ability to deliver", "bbox": [843.8, 809.2, 1562.5, 829.2]}, {"text": "more high-value applications that help our customers identify, track and manage assets,", "bbox": [843.8, 830.1, 1554.1, 850.0]}, {"text": "transactions and people.", "bbox": [843.8, 850.9, 1041.4, 870.8]}, {"text": "Gross profit margin for ESG in 2008 were significantly higher than in 2007 due to the", "bbox": [843.8, 890.5, 1521.5, 910.4]}, {"text": "margins of the software business added in late 2007, as a result of the Navis acquisition,", "bbox": [843.8, 911.3, 1552.1, 931.3]}, {"text": "being significantly higher than the hardware business we had in 2007.", "bbox": [843.8, 932.1, 1400.8, 952.1]}, {"text": "ESG results for the fourth quarter of 2008 reflect spending rates for all of the businesses", "bbox": [843.8, 971.7, 1552.2, 991.7]}, {"text": "acquired during 2007 and 2008 that comprise ESG. The operating expenses for ESG for", "bbox": [843.8, 992.6, 1543.4, 1012.5]}, {"text": "all of 2008 are not comparable to the operating expenses for 2007 because the operating", "bbox": [843.8, 1013.4, 1555.8, 1033.3]}, {"text": "expenses for 2007 do not include the financial results for all of those businesses.", "bbox": [843.8, 1034.2, 1491.9, 1054.2]}, {"text": "ESG’s fourth quarter results also reflect a reduction in operating expenses during the", "bbox": [843.8, 1055.1, 1528.4, 1075.0]}, {"text": "second half of the year. These cost reduction efforts reduced ESG’s employee count", "bbox": [843.8, 1075.9, 1519.2, 1095.8]}, {"text": "by approximately 40. Operating expenses for the fourth quarter and the full year", "bbox": [843.8, 1096.7, 1489.9, 1116.7]}, {"text": "reflect a write-down of assets in the amount of $142,920,000 related to our recent ESG", "bbox": [843.8, 1117.6, 1536.8, 1137.5]}, {"text": "acquisitions and intellectual property because of changes in valuations as a result of the", "bbox": [843.8, 1138.4, 1553.2, 1158.3]}, {"text": "current economic conditions and the business outlook.", "bbox": [843.8, 1159.2, 1283.0, 1179.2]}]}